sentences: Before his 5566 debut in 2002, every Soccer match in Taiwan both big and small, featured Wang Shao Wei on its players list.
On June 26, 2002, Shao Wei became the Soccer coach for one of the community activities Soccer teams.
In 2004, Shao Wei released a book called 明星入門100招 (100 Ways To Become A Star).
In December 2007, Wang Shao Wei promoted 5566's album, Bravo, in Singapore.
On November 18, 2007, fans helped him celebrate his 31st birthday, and unexpectedly gave him a 2 million dollar Lexus Alphard as a birthday present.

In March 2008 he changed his name from 王绍偉 to 王少偉 (the reading is still the same).
In 2008, Shao wei launched his first bakery shop, named Uncle Sam.
The same year he appeared in the movie Drifting Flowers.
In 2009, he launched his second shop- Uncle Sam's Junior, a branch of Uncle Sam's Bakery Cafe.
